---
title: Swedish-Style Ground Plant-Based Protein Meatballs with Creamy Gravy and Buttery Green Beans
description: Skip a trip to a certain Scandinavian shop and make these DIY ground protein meatballs at home! Soften seasoned breadcrumbs with a bit of milk for extra tender results.
